Package: fmir
Type: Package
Title: Access open weather data from the Finnish Meteorological Institute
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Mikko", "Marttila", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "mikmart@mikkomarttila.com")
Description: This package provides helper functions for easily accessing up to
    date, open weather data, made available by the Finnish Meteorological
    Institute. Use simple R syntax to create queries for the FMI API;
    download XML data from the API; and parse into a tidy R data frame.
    In order to use the open data API, you'll need to register with the Finnish
    Meteorological Institute. See https://en.ilmatieteenlaitos.fi/open-data for
    details.
URL: https://github.com/mikmart/fmir
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
